# Forza HTTPS
http://*       https://:splat 301!

# Forza dominio canonico (apex, senza www)
https://www.mexasrl.com/*  https://mexasrl.com/:splat 301!

# Reindirizza il vecchio dominio .it al .com
http://mexa.it/*           https://mexasrl.com/:splat 301!
https://mexa.it/*          https://mexasrl.com/:splat 301!
https://www.mexa.it/*      https://mexasrl.com/:splat 301!


# Opzionale (solo se un domani diventa SPA):
# /assets/*   /assets/:splat   200!
# /images/*   /images/:splat   200!
# /fonts/*    /fonts/:splat    200!
